quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  4,142,"“Ndithu achiphamaso akufuna kunyenga Allah koma Iye awalanga (chifukwa cha chinyengo chawocho). Ndipo akaimilira kupemphera Swala, amaimilira mwaulesi ndikungoonetsa anthu (kuti akupemphera). Ndipo satchula Allah koma pang’ono pokha"
  4,143,“Akungoyendayenda pakati pa awa ndi awa (pakati pa Asilamu ndi osakhulupirira). Iwo sali mbali iyi kapena mbali inayo. Ndipo amene Allah wamlekelera kuti asokere sungampezere njira yolungama
  4,144,"“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Musawachite osakhulupirira kukhala abwenzi anu kusiya okhulupirira (Asilamu), kodi mukufuna kuti Allah akhale ndi umboni woonekera pa inu (kuti ndinu oyipa)"
  4,145,“Ndithu achiphamaso adzakhala pansi penipeni pa Moto; ndipo sudzampeza mthandizi woimira iwo
  4,146,“Kupatula amene alapa (pambuyo pa uchiphamaso wawo); nakonza (makhalidwe awo) nadziphatika kwa Allah; namuyeretseranso Allah chipembedzo chawo. Choncho iwo ali pamodzi ndi okhulupirira. Ndipo Allah adzapatsa okhulupirira malipiro akulu
  4,147,"“Allah sangakulangeni ngati mumthokoze ndi kumkhulupirira. Ndithudi, Allah Ngolandira kuthokoza kwanu, ndiponso Ngodziwa"
  4,148,"“۞ Allah sakonda kutulutsa mawu ofalitsa kuipa (kwa anthu) kupatula yekhayo wachitiridwa zoipa. Ndipo Allah Ngwakumva, Ngodziwa"
  4,149,"“Ngati mungaonetse chabwino, kapena kuchibisa, kapena kukhululukira zoipa, (zoterozo ndizo zofunika), ndithu Allah Ngokhululuka ndiponso Ngokhoza"
  4,150,"“Ndithudi amene sakhulupirira Allah ndi atumiki Ake, ndikumafuna kulekanitsa pakati pa Allah ndi atumiki Ake, ndikumanena kuti: “Ena tikuwakhulupirira, koma ena tikuwakana,” ndikumafunanso kukhonza njira yapakati pa zimenezo"
  4,151,“Iwowo ndiosakhulupirira enieni. Ndipo osakhulupirira tawakonzera chilango choyalutsa
  4,152,"“Tsopano amene akhulupirira Allah ndi atumiki Ake, napanda kulekanitsa pakati pa aliyense wa iwo (koma nkuwakhulupirira onse), iwo adzawapatsa malipiro awo. Ndipo Allah Ngokhululuka kwambiri, Wachisoni chosatha"